{"type": "article", "id": 22689, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-02-23T07:30:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 23795, "name": "Atelier JMCA"}, {"id": 23744, "name": "有所"}, {"id": 23796, "name": "Néit"}, {"id": 23797, "name": "Cerno"}, {"id": 23798, "name": "ICRAVE"}, {"id": 23799, "name": "Shahar Nissim"}, {"id": 23800, "name": "Caz Hildebrand"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122216QUySl5vB9zuigpFh.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Work &amp; Turn table by Atelier JMCA</h2>\n<p>法国的设计工作室 Atelier JMCA 要为巴黎的烹饪俱乐部 FOODLAB 的办公室设计一张工作桌，要求既可以是工作桌，切割台，也能容纳所有人围在一起吃饭。最简单的方式是让这张桌子可以旋转，首先将桌腿沿着中轴旋转到 120 度，就可使桌面翻转，实现木板和切割台的转换。桌子的侧边有插口满足电子产品的需要，它同时是加长桌的插口，两边扩展后使桌面的长度超过 4 米。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105810QWumkapdObJVrCfX.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105811pN4oEgk5FmyciBAP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105811b0VrmMW1SeHgoyNG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021058126Z0XTEPzjFwrdipn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105812PwBTV03GbUpck8FO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>方糖沙发 by 有所</h2>\n<p>这是有所推出的方糖沙发，与昨日推荐的布丁沙发一样带着食物的甜蜜。沙发的整体像一个立方体，四根白蜡木腿连接了靠背和很厚的方形座位，温和而静谧。设计者称选用的中性色和硬木颜色都是低存在感的颜色，希望带给人默默的关爱。售价 1019 元，<a href=\"https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.1-c.w5003-11735453309.7.vtHuqk&amp;id=520444098938&amp;scene=taobao_shop\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105812x7GhdBSXgvVbLsU3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105813zS47HrVF1fKUlYt3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105813sMOF8Ufk0VnTClLr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105814ChpDaYg6SbeswNjc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105815YrpgcKGRq3Jbt7is.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Néit 旅行箱 by Néit</h2>\n<p>英国设计团队 Néit 推出了一款可折叠的行李箱，不用的时候就将行李箱两侧向内翻折，使原有的立体空间完全压缩成一个平面，就像衣服一样完全可以挂在晾衣杆上，大大节省占用的空间。这个旅行箱采用聚碳酸酯（PC）材料，表面有波浪花紋来增加强度，产品目前在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/neit/neit-revolutionary-smart-collapsible-hard-case-lug\">这里是众筹链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105815FAWDrHlYE7fU58sV.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66568483\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105816fxCu2LWpmTiUlqbB.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105818tDGOK9gSBFZvR4Xb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.96153846\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105818v0COazQVeKhsx136.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72307692\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105819w9jUFqh03mJSLHz2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61230769\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105819auLjVt1903ieFPoG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 22px; line-height: 30px; text-align: left; background-color: transparent;\">LI©HT by Cerno &amp; ICRAVE</span></h2>\n<p>这是两家设计品牌 Cerno 和 ICRAVE 联合推出的灯，一共有两种，都采用三角木架和金属灯罩的组合，不同只在于灯罩的长短和与支架的位置，一个用三角支架支撑，另一个像是滑到了下面。两盏灯都带有一点工业味道，适合暗色调的地方。灯罩有多种颜色，售价 1494 美元起，<a href=\"http://www.ylighting.com/cerno-imber-pendant-light.html\">这里是购买链接</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105820FX5zQOCiaurkPq7A.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105820kA5FxJtrwmEDNTfy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105821TPD2e83kOHaLpUBW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.05833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105821NiFvlMOuH3Z7zfc4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021058212rpbk8zatGiIMyJm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Egg ninjas by Shahar Nissim</h2>\n<p>这是一个帮助煮鸡蛋的小工具，由以色列设计师 Shahar Nissim 和以色列一家专门供应奇妙的产品的公司 monkey business 一起推出。它是用耐高温和耐水性好的硅胶材料做的，可以随着鸡蛋一起在锅里煮，手提的圆环除了控制移动，还可以帮助鸡蛋站立在桌面上，像是蒙上了一个忍者面具。有黑色和红色两种，售价 15 美元，<a href=\"http://www.mnkbusiness.com/egg-ninjas/\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021058224IyQc7ZP8gKF9axL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105822EcG7nUvIWw5ONdPz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105823iD0SEH6Fz5VUjkCy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105823J3VqNs1HpDrkXoj2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105823UAcYhy8dGEg0N5sW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55501222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h2>Geometry of Pasta by Caz Hildebrand </h2>\n<p>Geometry of Pasta 是由平面设计师 Caz Hildebrand 和主厨 Jacob Kenedy 一起创立的意面品牌，他们在 2010 年一起推出了一本关于烹饪的书。他们充分开发意大利面的各种形状设计出黑白两色的图案，在果酱和意面的包装上都体现出这种具有很强装饰感的“意面的几何学”。盒装意面中间开了一个小窗口，可以看到意面的形态，<a href=\"http://www.geometryofpasta.com\">他们的网站里有详细的介绍和购买途径。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021058241h6otkNBqLKwnP5m.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105824sKb6ixNCdZ924GaE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105825X0UxzDNfRZW8Ldhy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105825sGSLVcgy9oNnPMwe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105826SFDEBn2kcJmo7syz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105826KkTrJfZethWbYNw9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105827r01mV8sq2YCXPUiy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}